lant_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the_cure_troxy_tom_pallant_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the_cure_troxy_tom_pallant_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the_cure_troxy_tom_pallant_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the_cure_troxy_tom_pallant_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Cure">The Cure</a>将于本月将《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">Songs Of A Lost World</a> 》发行当晚的现场表演作为现场专辑发布。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="734" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-troxy-london-songs-of-a-lost-world-seventeen-seconds-setlist-footage-photos-pedro-pascal-3808927"><b>The Cure 在壮观的伦敦 Troxy 演出中完整演奏《失落世界之歌》并庆祝《十七秒》</b></a></li></ul><p>这张专辑名为“Songs Of A Live World Troxy London MMXXIV”，将于 12 月 13 日通过 Fiction/Polydor 以多种实体形式发行，乐队的所有版税将捐赠给慈善机构<a href="https://www.warchild.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">War Child</a> 。</p><p>除了一张单曲 CD 和一张单曲透明黑胶唱片外，还有双 CD 版本、单曲和双曲 LP 血红色黑胶唱片版本以及一张双曲 LP，其中包括 2 月 14 日推出的专辑的器乐版本。您可以预订你的副本<a href="https://thecure.lnk.to/SongsOfALostWorld" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDC0vzHpVo3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="1